olimits}aluminium-based silicon carbide bench and emitted laser beams with four different frequencies on three fiber ports to capture, cool, prepare, and detect atoms. The optical system, utilizing a compact three-layer optical-mechanical and thermal management design, passed environmental simulation tests and adapted to a special satellite-borne environment. The optical system stability meets the laser requirements of the clock.
